
Prerequisites:

cmake, opencv


To compile in the lab
——————————

run ./lab_config.sh
cd build
make

To compile on your own machine
———

cd build/
cmake ../
make


To run
——

In the build folder:
./sc image1 new_width new_height image2



//My way of running

cd Project\ ADT/Project\ ADT/code/
g++ src/main.cpp `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
cd build/
cmake ../
make 
./seg simple.png config.txt image2.png

 
